name: Rope Dining Chair - Black
description: Introducing the Rope Dining Chair – Black. The dining chairs pared back design showcases natural tactile textured rope, solid natural timber and a vintage shape. The seatpad and backrest are made from intricately woven rope, set in a solid teak wood frame. The timeless design that has been crafted to stand the test of time. Ideal for minimalists looking to incorporate textural interest into a space.
